/app/docs/nodes/audio.md:173:**Opt-out per Telegram group/topic:**
/app/docs/nodes/audio.md:175:- Set `channels.telegram.groups.<chatId>.disableAudioPreflight: true` to skip preflight transcript mention checks for that group.
